Cost-effectiveness of genetic testing in family members of patients with long-QT 
syndrome.

Perez MV(1), Kumarasamy NA, Owens DK, Wang PJ, Hlatky MA.

Author information:
(1)Center for Inherited Cardiovascular Disease, Stanford University Medical 
